  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "They scramble to get oil from the overturned diesel bowser",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that an oil tanker carrying 33000 liters of diesel which came from the Trincomalee IOC fuel depot to the Haputale oil depot has overturned on the road in the Panketiya area of \u200b\u200bHaputale this morning (11) and the local residents are scrambling to collect the spilled oil.",
        "The police say that the road has slipped and the lorry has overturned and no one has been injured.",
        "The police also say that they are making necessary arrangements to get the fuel from this bus to another bus.",
        "The police also say that the local residents will take away the oil cans that are going away."
      ],
